强制换行：   File → Other Settings → Default Settings → Editor → Code Style → Hard wrap at: 150

默认换行符：  File → Other Settings → Default Settings → Editor → Code Style → Line separator: Unix and OS X (\n)

Terminal：   File → Other Settings → Default Settings → Tools → Terminal → Shell path: git\bin\bash.exe

Ignored Schemas and DTDs:   File → Other Settings → Default Settings → Language & Frameworks → Schemas and DTDs → Ignored Schemas and DTDs

File and Code Templates:    File → Other Settings → Default Settings → Editor → File and Code Templates → Files → Class / Interface
/**
